<div class="excerpt_header snap_nopreview">
	<a title="" href="/Blog/Tech-FAQ/how-to-create-a-secure-business-vpn.html">How to Create a Secure Business VPN</a>
</div>
	<div style="float:left;margin-top:6px;"><img border="0" src="/img/blog/vangie.jpg" width="32px" height="32px"></div>
<div class="postdate">Posted: April 24, 2012 by Vangie Beal <a href='http://twitter.com/AuroraGG'><img src='/img/blog/twitter-bird.png' width='20px' height='13px' border='0' /></a></div>
<div style="clear:both;"></div>
<div style="padding-bottom: 25pt;" class="excerpt_subheader">
<div class="excerpt_subheader_right"><a href="/Blog/Tech-FAQ/how-to-create-a-secure-business-vpn.html"
