<div class="entry">
<img src=/imagesvr_ce/3625/Facebookscreen.jpg  style="float:left;margin:2px;width:300px;height:200px;"/>
<p>The movie "Field of Dreams," starring Kevin Costner, spawned one of the most well-known quotes of all time: "If you build it, he will come." &nbsp;</p>
<p> Costner builds a baseball field -- in the middle of a cornfield of all places -- and after a time thousands do come.&nbsp; The "build it and they will come" analogy has been used time and time again as the basis for starting a new business, developing new products and even in building online communities.</p></div>
