<div class="excerpt">
<div class="excerpt_header snap_nopreview">
	<a title="" href="/Blog/Tech-Opinion/children-and-technology-the-disappearing-digital-divide.html">Children and Technology: The Disappearing Digital Divide</a>
</div>
	<div style="float:left;margin-top:6px;"><img border="0" src="/img/blog/vangie.jpg" width="32px" height="32px"></div>
